---
title: Dilly Seared Scallops with Marinated Veggies and Lemon-Butter Risotto
description: Get ready for golden-brown seared scallops served atop a velvety  risotto. A snappy warm asparagus salad with burst baby tomatoes partners with this delicious combination for a gourmet meal right in your own home.
